  "A store sells T-shirts for $15 and hats for $10. A customer buys a total of 8 items and spends $100. Using the system t + h = 8 and 15t + 10h = 100, how many T-shirts and hats were bought?": "",
  "6 T-shirts and 2 hats": "",
  "4 T-shirts and 4 hats": "",
  "5 T-shirts and 3 hats": "",
  "3 T-shirts and 5 hats": "",
  "From t + h = 8: h = 8 - t. Substitute: 15t + 10(8 - t) = 100, 15t + 80 - 10t = 100, 5t = 20, t = 4. h = 4.": "",
  "Two friends have a combined age of 40. One is 6 years older than the other. The system is a + b = 40 and a = b + 6. What are their ages?": "",
  "20 and 20": "",
  "25 and 15": "",
  "22 and 18": "",
  "23 and 17": "",
  "Substitute a = b + 6: (b + 6) + b = 40, 2b + 6 = 40, 2b = 34, b = 17. a = 23.": "",
  "A farmer has chickens and cows. There are 20 heads and 56 legs total. Using h + c = 20 and 2h + 4c = 56, find the number of each animal.": "",
  "12 chickens and 8 cows": "",
  "8 chickens and 12 cows": "",
  "10 chickens and 10 cows": "",
  "15 chickens and 5 cows": "",
  "From h + c = 20: h = 20 - c. Substitute: 2(20 - c) + 4c = 56, 40 - 2c + 4c = 56, 2c = 16, c = 8. h = 12.": "",
  "A movie theater sold 200 tickets. Adult tickets cost $12 and child tickets cost $7. Total revenue was $1,900. Using a + c = 200 and 12a + 7c = 1900, how many adult tickets were sold?": "",
  "100": "",
  "150": "",
  "80": "",
  "120": "",
  "From a + c = 200: c = 200 - a. Substitute: 12a + 7(200 - a) = 1900, 12a + 1400 - 7a = 1900, 5a = 500, a = 100.": "",
